verbose_text: Structural similarities of PLPs to deubiquitinating enzymes showed that PLPs not only function as deubiquitinating enzymes, but are also able to block induction of several endogenous proinflammatory cytokines, including IFNbeta, CCL5 and CXCL10 98.
